### Test All Authentication Schemes

@hostname = https://localhost:7142

### ========================================
### PUBLIC ENDPOINT (No Authentication)
### ========================================

GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/public

### ========================================
### ALL SCHEMES ENDPOINT
### ========================================

### Using Basic Authentication
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/all
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Using API Key Authentication
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/all
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

### Using JWT Bearer Authentication (get token first from /connect/token)
# POST {{hostname}}/connect/token
# Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
# 
# grant_type=password&username=admin&password=password123

### ========================================
### BASIC AUTHENTICATION ONLY
### ========================================

### Valid Basic Auth
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/basic
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Invalid - Using API Key (should fail)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/basic
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

### ========================================
### API KEY AUTHENTICATION ONLY
### ========================================

### Valid API Key
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/apikey
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

### Invalid - Using Basic Auth (should fail)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/apikey
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### ========================================
### JWT OR API KEY AUTHENTICATION
### ========================================

### Using API Key
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/jwt-or-apikey
X-API-Key: prod-api-key-67890

### Using Basic Auth (should fail)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/jwt-or-apikey
Authorization: Basic dXNlcjp1c2VyMTIz

### ========================================
### WEATHERFORECAST ENDPOINT (All Schemes)
### ========================================

### Using Basic Authentication
GET {{hostname}}/weatherforecast
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Using API Key Authentication
GET {{hostname}}/weatherforecast
X-API-Key: readonly-api-key-11111

###
# ========================================
# AUTHENTICATION SCHEMES SUMMARY
# ========================================
#
# 1. JWT Bearer (default scheme)
#    - Get token from /connect/token
#    - Use: Authorization: Bearer {token}
#
# 2. Basic Authentication
#    - Use: Authorization: Basic {base64(username:password)}
#    - Test credentials:
#      * admin:password123 (YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=)
#      * user:user123 (dXNlcjp1c2VyMTIz)
#
# 3. API Key Authentication
#    - Use: X-API-Key: {api-key}
#    - Test keys:
#      * dev-api-key-12345 (Admin - all scopes)
#      * prod-api-key-67890 (User - read/write)
#      * readonly-api-key-11111 (Reader - read only)
#
# ========================================
# AUTHORIZATION POLICIES
# ========================================
#
# - DefaultPolicy: JWT + Basic + API Key
# - JwtOnly: JWT Bearer only
# - BasicOnly: Basic Auth only
# - ApiKeyOnly: API Key only
# - JwtOrApiKey: JWT Bearer or API Key
# ========================================